WEBVTT

00:01.634 --> 00:02.799
This is Yasuho.

00:02.956 --> 00:06.615
A 22-year-old living in Tokyo, and she's just waking up to start her day.

00:10.893 --> 00:14.775
She lives alone in this newly built 1k apartment and like many Japanese,...

00:15.033 --> 00:18.121
...she prefers to take a bath at night just before she goes to sleep.

00:21.454 --> 00:22.197
Oh, nice!

00:22.389 --> 00:23.636
She's sporting mop slippers.

00:31.011 --> 00:32.858
I guess she doesn't eat breakfast in her apartment.

